          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/41751009/" class=" " title="柳絮">柳絮</a>
                (大胖)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="28329110">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">第一页第二段有一处误译：
及时确定了自己的兴趣之后，其结果便是这本主要是涉及知识论的书，即考察我们能说知道或有理由相信的那部分哲学分支。
查原文为（http://www.filedu.com/jskorupskiintroductionto.pdf）：
The upshot, given his interests at the time, is that the book is mainly concerned with epistemology - the branch of philosophy which investigates what we can be said to know or reasonably believe.</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-08-29 13:10</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                第一页第二段有一处误译：
<blockquote><q>及时确定了自己的兴趣之后，其结果便是这本主要是涉及知识论的书，即考察我们能说知道或有理由相信的那部分哲学分支。</q></blockquote>
查原文为（<a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.filedu.com/jskorupskiintroductionto.pdf" target="_blank">http://www.filedu.com/jskorupskiintroductionto.pdf</a>）：
<blockquote><q>The upshot, given his interests at the time, is that the book is mainly concerned with epistemology - the branch of philosophy which investigates what we can be said to know or reasonably believe.</q></blockquote>
